import React from "react";

const PorcoRossoComendo = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      width="946"
      height="537"
      viewBox="0 0 946 537"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    >
      <rect width="946" height="537" rx="40" fill="url(#pattern0)" />
      <defs>
        <pattern
          id="pattern0"
          patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
          width="1"
          height="1"
        >
          <use
            xlinkHref="#image0_1_10"
            transform="matrix(0.001 0 0 0.00176164 0 -0.0249683)"
          />
        </pattern>
        <image
          id="image0_1_10"
          width="1000"
          height="596"
        />
      </defs>
    </svg>
  );
};

export { PorcoRossoComendo };
